---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Leadership Development for Finance Leaders | StratumCore"
  description="Practical leadership programmes for finance leaders in mining and resources. Build influence, drive decisions, and step beyond the scorekeeper role."
  canonical="https://www.stratumcore.com.au/leadership-development"
  ogImageAlt="Leadership Development — StratumCore"
>

  <Nav />

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       1. PAGE HERO
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section
    class="hero-dark flex items-end relative overflow-hidden"
    style="min-height: 65vh;"
    aria-label="Leadership Development"
  >
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
      style="
        background-image:
          radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 65% at 95% 10%, rgba(0,201,187,0.06) 0%, transparent 55%),
          radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 50% at 5%  85%, rgba(212,117,26,0.04) 0%, transparent 50%),
          linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 1px, transparent 1px),
          linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 1px, transparent 1px);
        background-size: auto, auto, 72px 72px, 72px 72px;
      "
      aria-hidden="true"
    ></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-site mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 pb-20 pt-[72px] w-full">
      <div class="max-w-4xl fade-up">

        <p class="page-label mb-6">Leadership Development</p>
        <span class="teal-rule mb-8 block"></span>

        <h1
          class="font-serif font-bold text-white leading-none"
          style="font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 4.75rem); letter-spacing: -0.03em; max-width: 36rem; line-height: 1.05;"
        >
          Leadership development for finance professionals.
        </h1>

        <p
          class="font-serif font-bold mt-6"
          style="font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.6vw, 1.25rem); color: #00C9BB; letter-spacing: -0.01em;"
        >
          Beyond technical competence.
        </p>

        <p
          class="font-serif mt-4 leading-relaxed"
          style="font-size: clamp(0.9375rem, 1.2vw, 1.0625rem); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.50); max-width: 40rem; line-height: 1.75;"
        >
          Most finance leaders are promoted for being technically excellent. Then
          they're expected to influence strategy, manage stakeholders, and lead
          through uncertainty — with no training for any of it. We fix that.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       2. THE PROBLEM — Bold typographic layout, no cards
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-white py-24 lg:py-32" aria-label="The gap we close">
    <div class="max-w-site mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10">

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-start">

        <!-- Left: label + heading -->
        <div class="fade-up">
          <p class="page-label mb-5" style="color: #00C9BB;">The gap we close</p>
          <h2
            class="font-serif font-bold text-body"
            style="font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.2vw, 3rem); letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 1.08; max-width: 22rem;"
          >
            Finance leaders who can think. Not just report.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: prose -->
        <div class="fade-up lg:pt-2" style="transition-delay: 80ms;">
          <!-- Pull-quote style accent line -->
          <div class="mb-8" style="width: 3rem; height: 2px; background: #00C9BB; border-radius: 1px;"></div>
          <p
            class="font-serif leading-relaxed mb-6"
            style="font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.4vw, 1.125rem); color: rgba(34,34,34,0.75); line-height: 1.85;"
          >
            In mining finance, the pressure to close the books, hit reporting
            deadlines, and manage variance commentary is relentless. Most teams
            become expert scorekeepers — technically sharp, but operating at arm's
            length from the decisions that actually move the business.
          </p>
          <p
            class="font-serif leading-relaxed"
            style="font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.4vw, 1.125rem); color: rgba(34,34,34,0.75); line-height: 1.85;"
          >
            The gap isn't technical. It's the ability to walk into an operational
            review and change the conversation — to reframe a cost problem as a
            capital allocation problem, or push back on a project business case with
            credibility. That's a different skill set. And it can be taught.
          </p>

          <!-- Emphasis callout -->
          <blockquote
            class="mt-10 pl-6 font-serif font-bold"
            style="border-left: 3px solid #00C9BB; font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.6vw, 1.375rem); color: #1C1C1E; letter-spacing: -0.015em; line-height: 1.4;"
          >
            "The best finance people don't report on decisions. They're in the room
            when the decision is being made."
          </blockquote>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       3. WHAT WE OFFER — Light grey, programme cards
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-24 lg:py-32" style="background: #F2F2F2;" aria-label="Programmes">
    <div class="max-w-site mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10">

      <div class="mb-16 fade-up">
        <p class="page-label mb-4">Programmes</p>
        <h2
          class="font-serif font-bold text-body"
          style="font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.75rem); letter-spacing: -0.025em; line-height: 1.1; max-width: 28rem;"
        >
          How we work with you.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Programme cards — 3-column on lg, stacked below -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-px" style="background: #DCDCDC;">

        <!-- Card 1: Coaching -->
        <article class="programme-card bg-white p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col fade-up" style="transition-delay: 0ms;">
          <div
            class="programme-icon mb-6 flex items-center justify-center"
            style="width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 3px; background: rgba(0,201,187,0.10);"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <!-- Person icon -->
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
              <circle cx="10" cy="7" r="3.5" stroke="#00C9BB" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <path d="M3 18c0-3.866 3.134-7 7-7s7 3.134 7 7" stroke="#00C9BB" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="tile-number mb-4">01</p>
          <h3
            class="font-serif font-bold text-body mb-4"
            style="font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 1.5vw, 1.3rem); letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1.2;"
          >
            One-on-one executive coaching
          </h3>
          <p
            class="font-serif leading-relaxed flex-1"
            style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: rgba(34,34,34,0.62); line-height: 1.75;"
          >
            For senior finance leaders navigating complexity, transitions, or new
            roles. Structured over three to six months, with a clear development
            agenda from session one.
          </p>
        </article>

        <!-- Card 2: Workshops -->
        <article class="programme-card bg-white p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col fade-up" style="transition-delay: 80ms;">
          <div
            class="programme-icon mb-6 flex items-center justify-center"
            style="width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 3px; background: rgba(0,201,187,0.10);"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <!-- Group icon -->
            <svg width="22" height="20" viewBox="0 0 22 20" fill="none">
              <circle cx="11" cy="7" r="3" stroke="#00C9BB" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <circle cx="4"  cy="7" r="2.5" stroke="#00C9BB" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <circle cx="18" cy="7" r="2.5" stroke="#00C9BB" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <path d="M1 18c0-2.761 1.343-5 3-5" stroke="#00C9BB" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <path d="M21 18c0-2.761-1.343-5-3-5" stroke="#00C9BB" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <path d="M5 18c0-3.314 2.686-6 6-6s6 2.686 6 6" stroke="#00C9BB" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="tile-number mb-4">02</p>
          <h3
            class="font-serif font-bold text-body mb-4"
            style="font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 1.5vw, 1.3rem); letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1.2;"
          >
            Team-based leadership workshops
          </h3>
          <p
            class="font-serif leading-relaxed flex-1"
            style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: rgba(34,34,34,0.62); line-height: 1.75;"
          >
            Half-day or full-day facilitated sessions on influence, communication,
            and commercial thinking. Designed for finance teams who need to work
            better with the business, not just within it.
          </p>
        </article>

        <!-- Card 3: FBP Academy -->
        <article class="programme-card bg-white p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col fade-up" style="transition-delay: 160ms;">
          <div
            class="programme-icon mb-6 flex items-center justify-center"
            style="width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 3px; background: rgba(0,201,187,0.10);"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <!-- Layers/programme icon -->
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
              <path d="M2 5l8-3 8 3-8 3-8-3z" stroke="#00C9BB" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M2 10l8 3 8-3" stroke="#00C9BB" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <path d="M2 15l8 3 8-3" stroke="#00C9BB" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="tile-number mb-4">03</p>
          <h3
            class="font-serif font-bold text-body mb-4"
            style="font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 1.5vw, 1.3rem); letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1.2;"
          >
            Finance Business Partner Academy
          </h3>
          <p
            class="font-serif leading-relaxed flex-1 mb-6"
            style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: rgba(34,34,34,0.62); line-height: 1.75;"
          >
            The flagship five-module programme that closes the gap between technical
            accounting competence and genuine business partnering — structured,
            sequenced, and built for mining finance.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/finance-business-partner-academy"
            class="font-serif font-bold inline-flex items-center gap-2 hover:gap-3 mt-auto"
            style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #00C9BB; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.01em; transition: gap 0.2s ease;"
          >
            See full programme details
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M2 7h10M8 3l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </article>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       4. DESIGNED FOR MINING — Dark, three-column stat-style
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section
    class="hero-dark py-24 lg:py-32 relative overflow-hidden"
    style="background-color: #1C1C1E; background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 70% at 50% 110%, rgba(0,201,187,0.05) 0%, transparent 60%);"
    aria-label="Designed for mining"
  >
    <div class="max-w-site mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 relative z-10">

      <div class="mb-16 fade-up">
        <p class="page-label mb-4">Why it works</p>
        <h2
          class="font-serif font-bold text-white"
          style="font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.75rem); letter-spacing: -0.025em; line-height: 1.1; max-width: 34rem;"
        >
          Built for the operational reality of mining finance.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 lg:gap-16">

        <div class="mining-stat-item fade-up" style="transition-delay: 0ms;">
          <div class="mb-5" style="width: 3rem; height: 2px; background: rgba(0,201,187,0.50); border-radius: 1px;"></div>
          <p
            class="font-serif font-bold text-white"
            style="font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.6vw, 1.375rem); letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1.35;"
          >
            Delivered in formats that work around site rosters and remote teams.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mining-stat-item fade-up" style="transition-delay: 90ms;">
          <div class="mb-5" style="width: 3rem; height: 2px; background: rgba(0,201,187,0.50); border-radius: 1px;"></div>
          <p
            class="font-serif font-bold text-white"
            style="font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.6vw, 1.375rem); letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1.35;"
          >
            Content grounded in real mining finance scenarios — not generic MBA
            theory.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mining-stat-item fade-up" style="transition-delay: 180ms;">
          <div class="mb-5" style="width: 3rem; height: 2px; background: rgba(0,201,187,0.50); border-radius: 1px;"></div>
          <p
            class="font-serif font-bold text-white"
            style="font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.6vw, 1.375rem); letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1.35;"
          >
            Facilitator has worked in the roles your leaders hold.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       5. CLOSING CTA
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section
    class="py-24 lg:py-32 relative overflow-hidden"
    aria-label="Contact"
    style="background: #00C9BB;"
  >
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
      style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 60px 60px;"
      aria-hidden="true"
    ></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-site mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 text-center fade-up">
      <h2
        class="font-serif font-bold mb-8 mx-auto"
        style="font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 3rem); color: #1C1C1E; letter-spacing: -0.025em; line-height: 1.2; max-width: 38rem;"
      >
        Find out how we can develop your finance leadership capability.
      </h2>
      <a
        href="mailto:wen@stratumcore.com.au"
        class="font-serif font-bold inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 rounded-sm"
        style="background: #1C1C1E; color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 0.9375rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-decoration: none; box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(28,28,30,0.2); transition: background 0.18s ease, transform 0.18s cubic-bezier(0.34,1.56,0.64,1), box-shadow 0.18s ease;"
        onmouseover="this.style.background='#2d2d30'; this.style.transform='translateY(-2px)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 8px 24px rgba(28,28,30,0.35)'"
        onmouseout="this.style.background='#1C1C1E'; this.style.transform='translateY(0)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 4px 16px rgba(28,28,30,0.2)'"
      >
        Book a call
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M2 8h12M9 3l5 5-5 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <p
        class="font-serif mt-5"
        style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgba(28,28,30,0.55);"
      >
        wen@stratumcore.com.au &nbsp;·&nbsp; Brisbane, QLD, Australia
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .tile-number {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #00C9BB;
  }

  .programme-card {
    border-top: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.22s ease;
  }
  .programme-card:hover {
    border-top-color: #00C9BB;
  }
</style>

<script>
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver(entries => {
    entries.forEach(e => {
      if (e.isIntersecting) { e.target.classList.add('visible'); observer.unobserve(e.target); }
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.07, rootMargin: '0px 0px -40px 0px' });

  document.querySelectorAll('.fade-up').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
  setTimeout(() => document.querySelectorAll('.fade-up').forEach(el => el.classList.add('visible')), 80);
</script>
